msgstr "Lecture auto dernière station au démarrage"

msgid "Bitrate"
msgstr "Débit binaire"

msgid "Changes"
msgstr "Changements"

msgid "Channel Mode"
msgstr "Mode canal"

msgid "Choose a file"
msgstr "Choisir un fichier"

msgid ""
"Click here to resume window. To quit Tuner, pause playback and close the "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Cliquez ici pour reprendre la fenêtre. Pour quitter Tuner, mettez en pause "
"la lecture et fermez la fenêtre."

msgid "Codec"
msgstr "Codec"

msgid "Container Format"
msgstr "Format conteneur"

msgid "Copy Stream-URI to clipboard"
msgstr "Copier l'URI de flux dans presse-papiers"

#, c-format
msgid "Could not get random station: %s"
msgstr "Impossible d’obtenir une station aléatoire : %s"

msgid "Cycle through the metadata from the playing stream"
msgstr "Parcourir les métadonnées du flux en cours de lecture"

msgid "Dark mode"
msgstr "Thème sombre"

msgid "Data Provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur de données"

msgid "Date Time"
msgstr "Date Heure"

msgid "Default"
msgstr "Par défaut"

msgid "Discover"
msgstr "Découvrir"

msgid "Discover more stations"
msgstr "Découvrir plus de stations"

msgid "Do not participate in Station voting"
msgstr "Ne pas participer au vote de station"

#, c-format
msgid ""
"Double click to shuffle through %1$u stations,\n"
"one, every ten minutes, for %2$u days"
msgstr ""
"Double-cliquer pour parcourir %1$u stations,\n"
"une, toutes les dix minutes, pendant %2$u jours"

msgid "Encoder"
msgstr "Encodeur"

msgid "Encoder Version"
msgstr "Version encodeur"

msgid "Eras"
msgstr "Années"

#, c-format
msgid "Error reading file: %s"
msgstr "Erreur de lecture fichier : %s"

msgid "Error while trying to autoplay, aborting…"
msgstr "Erreur lors de la tentative de lecture automatique, interruption…"

#, c-format
msgid "Error: %s"
msgstr "Erreur : %s"

msgid "Explore"
msgstr "Explorer"

msgid "Export Starred Stations to Playlist"
msgstr "Exporter stations étoilées vers playlist"

msgid "Extended Comment"
msgstr "Commentaire étendu"

msgid ""
"Fast cycle through the metadata from the playing stream if show stream info "
"is enabled"
msgstr ""
"Parcourir rapidement les métadonnées du flux en cours de lecture si les "
"informations de flux sont activées"

msgid "Faster cycling through stream info"
msgstr "Parcourir plus vite les infos du flux"

msgid "Favicon address"
msgstr "Adresse d'icône favorite"

msgid "Genre"
msgstr "Genre"

msgid "Genres"
msgstr "Genres"

msgid "Has CRC"
msgstr "Possède CRC"

msgid "History"
msgstr "Historique"

msgid "Homepage"
msgstr "Page d'accueil"

msgid "Homepage address"
msgstr "Adresse page d'accueil"

msgid ""
"If checked, your starred and streamed stations will not be used to calculate "
"the Station index popularity vote, nor the popular and trending stations"
msgstr ""
"Si cochée, vos stations favorites et diffusées ne seront pas utilisées pour "
"calculer le vote de popularité de l’indice de station, ni les stations "
"populaires et tendance"

msgid ""
"If enabled, when Tuner starts it will automatically start to play the last "
"played station"
msgstr ""
"Si activé, lorsque Tuner démarre, il commencera automatiquement à lire la "
"dernière station lue"

msgid "If enabled, when Tuner starts it will open to the starred stations view"
msgstr ""
"Si activé, lorsque Tuner démarre, il s’ouvrira sur la vue des stations "
"favorites"

msgid "Image"
msgstr "Image"

msgid "Import Station UUIDs as Starred Stations"
msgstr "Importer des UUID de stations en tant que stations favorites"

